                <h1>Understanding the Book of Isaiah: Prophecies and Messages</h1>
                <p>The Book of Isaiah is a prophetic text in the Bible attributed to the prophet Isaiah. It addresses themes of judgment, repentance, and hope, foretelling both the destruction of Israel due to disobedience and the promise of salvation through a coming Messiah. Its vivid imagery and calls for social justice resonate throughout history.</p>
